text: Coop & Cami Ask the World is an American comedy television series. It was created by Boyce Bugliari and Jamie McLaughlin. The series premiered on on October 12, 2018. It stars Dakota Lotus and Ruby Rose Turner as Coop and Cami Wrather, two middle school-aged siblings who crowdsource their decision-making online. The series ran for two seasons, airing its final episode on September 11, 2020.
